data.description:
PRICED TO SELL with Instant EQUITY for new owners.  Nestled in the quiet community of Hidden Creek, this charming 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home was recently built in 2019 and boasts modern conveniences throughout. The amenity-rich community is equipped with a gorgeous clubhouse, swimming pool, playground, and multiple walking trails! Upon arrival, you're greeted by the home's charming curb appeal and the cozy front porch. Inside, vinyl plank flooring flows throughout the bright and airy, two story foyer and the open living space. Break out your inner chef in the gourmet kitchen with subway tile backsplash, modern gray cabinets, and a large breakfast bar. The entry level also highlights a formal dining space, large bedroom and full bathroom. Upstairs, you'll find the spacious owner's suite with vaulted ceiling, separate sitting room and ''spa-like'' en suite bathroom with his and her vanities. Two additional bedrooms with a Jack and Jill bathroom are also situated on the second level. A versatile loft area can be utilized as a second living space, home office or playroom. Featuring over 2,700 square feet of living space, this home has been beautifully maintained and is ready for a new family to make memories! Priced to sell, it won't last long so schedule your private tour today! 

*Seller is ready to contribute $10,000 TOWARDS PAINT, RATE BUYDOWN, and/or CLOSING COSTS with a full price offer!!!

**Seller has an assumable VA loan with a percentage rate of 5.99%.
